OL,3,CLorry deaths ringleader ordered to pay
OL,4,Cthousands to victims' families
OL,6,FThe ringleader of a people smuggling
OL,7,Fgang has been ordered to pay thousands
OL,8,Fin compensation to the families of
OL,9,Fpeople found dead in the back of a
OL,10,Florry in Essex.
OL,12,FThirty nine Vietnamese men, women and
OL,13,Fchildren were found dead in a
OL,14,Frefrigerated trailer in Purfleet in
OL,15,FOctober 2019.
OL,17,FA hearing took place on 20 December at
OL,18,Fthe Central Criminal Court during
OL,19,Fwhich the available assets of
OL,20,Fconspiracy ringleader Ronan Hughes
OL,21,Fwere decided upon.
