OL,3,CLorry deaths ringleader ordered to pay
OL,4,Cthousands to victims' families
OL,6,FAt a previous hearing a month earlier,
OL,7,FHughes gave evidence that the property
OL,8,Fhe had built on land belonging to his
OL,9,Fparents in Ireland was not an
OL,10,Favailable asset for confiscation
OL,11,Fproceedings.
OL,13,FBut a judge at the Central Criminal
OL,14,FCourt found that the property in
OL,15,Fquestion was indeed an available asset
OL,16,Fand made a confiscation order
OL,17,Ftotalling #182,078.90 all to be paid
OL,18,Fin compensation.
