OL,3,CLorry deaths ringleader ordered to pay
OL,4,Cthousands to victims' families
OL,6,FIt means that as a result of the
OL,7,Ffinancial investigation into all
OL,8,Fconcerned, a total of #283,802.58 has
OL,9,Fbeen ordered to be paid to the 39
OL,10,Ffamilies.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Louise
OL,13,FMetcalfe said: "Following the
OL,14,Fconclusion of criminal proceedings and
OL,15,Fthe group being sentenced to a total
OL,16,Fof 117 years in prison, our final act
OL,17,Fhas been to pursue Hughes for his ill-
OL,18,Fgotten gains.
