OL,3,CLorry deaths ringleader ordered to pay
OL,4,Cthousands to victims' families
OL,6,F"We know he ` and his associates `
OL,7,Ftreated this operation as a lucrative
OL,8,Fbusiness and it would not have been
OL,9,Facceptable to anyone at Essex Police
OL,10,Fto conclude our work at this group's
OL,11,Fconviction.
OL,13,F"This money will be divided between
OL,14,Fthe Vietnamese families who continue
OL,15,Fto feel the devastating loss of their
OL,16,Floved ones.
OL,18,F"It will do little to help heal their
OL,19,Floss, I know this, but I do truly hope
OL,20,Fit will allow them to begin to move
OL,21,Fforward."
