OL,3,CLorry deaths ringleader ordered to pay
OL,4,Cthousands to victims' families
OL,6,FOn the day the 39 victims were
OL,7,Fdiscovered, Hughes left Thurrock and
OL,8,Fboarded a plane back to Ireland.
OL,10,FHe was issued as a wanted man on 29
OL,11,FOctober 2019, but he remained in his
OL,12,Fhome in County Monaghan in the
OL,13,FRepublic of Ireland, where Essex
OL,14,FPolice were unable to arrest him
OL,15,Fwithout a European Arrest Warrant.
OL,17,FOn 20 April 2020, the European Arrest
OL,18,FWarrant was granted, and Hughes was
OL,19,Fbrought back to Essex.
